    oc:differentia "Creates new PowerPoint presentations from scratch via html2pptx, creates presentations from templates via rearrange/inventory/replace scripts, edits existing presentations via OOXML unpack/edit/repack, and analyzes presentation content through text extraction, thumbnails, and visual inspection" ;
